The paper discusses monitoring of cloud infrastructures, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses energy efficiency and optimization, which is related to Software Engineering (cs.SE) and Computer Engineering (cs.CE). The monitoring frameworks presented in the paper involve collecting and analyzing data, which is related to Systems and Control (cs.SY) and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI).
